<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Paws and Collections</title>

<style>
body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: "Arial Rounded MT Bold", sans-serif;
    background: #ffe6ef;
    color: #5a3b3b;
}

/* Top header */
header {
    background: #ffb6c1;
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: white;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
}

/* Squishy paw corner */
.paw {
    position: fixed;
    top: 10px;
    right: 10px;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: pink;
    border-radius: 50% 50% 40% 40%;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
}

/* Intro box */
.intro {
    margin: 40px auto;
    width: 80%;
    background: #fff0f5;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 18px;
}

/* Sections */
.section {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 20px;
    margin: 40px;
}

.card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 20px;
    width: 200px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    transition: transform 0.2s;
}

.card:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
}

footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
    background: #ffb6c1;
    color: white;
    margin-top: 50px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
🍓 Paws and Collections 🐾
</header>

<!-- squishy paw -->
<div class="paw"></div>

<div class="intro">
<h2>Hi there! 💗</h2>
<p>You can call me <b>Kemi / Remi</b> 🐱✨<br>
Welcome to my cozy handmade shop full of strawberries, cats, and soft little joys 🍓</p>
</div>

<div class="section">

<div class="card">
<h3>🧶 Crochet</h3>
<p>Soft handmade cuties stitched with love</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>🐱 Plushies</h3>
<p>Squishy friends for hugs & naps</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>💎 Bracelets</h3>
<p>Berry sweet wrist accessories</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>🎒 Bags</h3>
<p>Cute everyday carry styles</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>🎉 Birthday</h3>
<p>Party kits full of pink joy</p>
</div>

</div>

<footer>
Made with love 🍓 Paws and Collections 🐾
</footer>

</body>
</html>